# Design Document – AffordMed React App

## 🧱 Architecture
- Functional Components
- Routing via React Router DOM
- Two Pages: Home and About

## ⚙️ Technologies
- React (create-react-app)
- react-router-dom

## 🔁 Routing
- `/` → Home
- `/about` → About

## 🧠 Data
- No API or backend used
- Future use: `useState`, `localStorage` or API

## 💡 Assumptions
- No login or form required
- Simple navigation between pages

## 🔮 Future Enhancements
- Add dynamic content via API
- Add login & error boundary
